WHAT IS THIS THING?
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
The ancient worm game but it has...

    32 colors screens
    33 levels
    Superb SFX
    Work even on 1.3 Amigas
    Hi-score saving

and much important

    An useful level editor, so you can create up to 100 custom levels!
    You can use your custom SFX



KEYS IN GAME
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
Cursor keys/Joystick to change menus
Left Alt/Fire to select a menu
P key to pause
Esc key to quit the game (only while you are playing)

Keys in game are (if keyboard mode is active):
  to move the worm use Cursor Keys
  to press fire use Left Alt



SWITCHES
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
MAIN MENU

.->START        to play the game
|
|->OPTIONS      to choose your best configuration, and in particular
|  |
|  |->ORIGINAL/CUSTOM LEVELS   to choose original or custom levels
|  |
|  |->ORIGINAL/CUSTOM SFX      to choose original or custom sfx
|  |
|  |->JOYSTICK/KEYBOARD   to choose the type of control (joystick/keyboard)
|  |
|  `->MAIN MENU           to came back to MAIN MENU
|
|->HIGH SCORE   to view the high-scores screen
|
|->ABOUT        some infos about the authors and the game
|
`->QUIT         guess what?



HOW USE YOUR OWN SFX
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
Easy, copy your samples (in IFF format) into directory "CustomSFX", where

    00.sfx
    01.sfx
    02.sfx
will be the "dead" sounds (when the worm collides with itself, there are no
more lifes etc.)

    03.sfx
    04.sfx
    05.sfx
will be the "win" sounds (when you finish a level)

    06.sfx
    07.sfx
    08.sfx
will be the "eat" sounds (when the worm eats a fruit)

    09.sfx
will be the "Press Fire" sound

NOTE! YOU CAN CHANGE ONLY THE CUSTOM SFX, NOT THE ORIGINAL SFX AND NOT EVEN
THE MAIN MENU MUSIC ETC



IMPORTANT
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
- You can hear the main menu music only if you have enough CHIP memory (and
kickstart 2.0 or higher).

- Who  wants  to  create  the  own  leves,  it's  better  that  read  the
LevelEditor.doc

- Only  if you press the QUIT option from the MAIN MENU, the game save the
high-score



SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
    Any Amiga with at least 512K of CHIP and 512K of FAST (the minimum
    requirement is about 390 Kbytes of CHIP RAM and 270 Kbytes of FAST RAM)
    and kickstart 1.2 or higher
    DiskFont.library
    IconX, Execute and Assign commands



HOW TO INSTALL
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
    Double-click on the icon named "Vermone2_Install"



